cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper is about a reinforcement learning method for recommendation systems, which involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, and data science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper also discusses the efficiency and practicality of the proposed method, which relates to the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
